LOS ANGELES=20

Governor Gray Davis today signed Executive Order D-39-01, which authorizes=20
the California Department of Water Resources (DWR) to implement voluntary,=20
emergency load curtailment programs for commercial, industrial or other larg=
e=20
businesses. In exchange for agreeing to reduce electricity usage during powe=
r=20
emergencies, the DWR will offer financial incentives to participating=20
customers.=20

