Davis said. "Commercial load curtailment programs can help mitigate and even=
=20
avoid blackouts. Therefore, I am ordering the Department of Water Resources=20
to implement a program that allows businesses to receive compensation if the=
y=20
voluntarily agree to reduce their energy consumption during peak periods."

