load curtailment programs currently offered by the California Independent=20
System Operator, the Public Utilities Commission, and the Investor-Owned=20
Utilities.=20

The DWR and the ISO will implement the programs for Summer 2001 and Summer=20
2002 and the DWR will finance the customer incentives. The incentives will b=
